{"word":"G5003 - ταλαιπωρέω - talaipōréō - tal-ahee-po-reh'-o - Be afflicted","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ταλαιπωρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>talaipōréō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>tal-ahee-po-reh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be afflicted"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - துயரப்படு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to toil heavily, to endure labors and hardships; to be afflicted; to feel afflicted and miserable"},{"paragraph":"2. to afflict"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G5005 - ταλαίπωρος - talaípōros - tal-ah'-ee-po-ros/5005\">G5005</a>; to <i>be wretched</i>, that is, <i>realize</i> one&rsquo;s own <i>misery:</i> - be afflicted."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}